      <title>印度法院下令各邦与干旱首都共享水资源</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/indian-court-orders-states-to-share-water-with-parched-capital</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度最高法院周四下令邻近各州增加对首都的供水，以帮助缓解因持续热浪造成的严重缺水现象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/indian-court-orders-states-to-share-water-with-parched-capital</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 13:05:47 GMT</pubDate>
