    <item>
      <title>印度出口民调引发批评、眼泪和调查呼吁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/india-s-exit-polls-were-wrong-prompting-criticism-apologies-investigations</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度出口民调结果严重失准，预测总理纳伦德拉·莫迪领导的政党将在选举中取得压倒性胜利，此举引发民调公司本周公开道歉，并呼吁对可能存在的操纵行为进行调查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/india-s-exit-polls-were-wrong-prompting-criticism-apologies-investigations</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 10:35:36 GMT</pubDate>
